            </div>
          </article>
<article class="card" role="listitem" data-price="249.99" data-sale="219.99">
  <a class="media" href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel-coolant-filtration-system-for-2013-2018-dodge-cummins-67l.html">
    <img src="/mm5/graphics/00000001/6/_DSC3320_1200x800.jpg" alt="">
