              <img src="/mm5/graphics/00000001/7/_DSC1833-web_1200x800.webp" alt="">
              <div class="disc-badge" aria-hidden="true">%</div>
            </a>
            <div class="body">
              <h3 class="name">
                <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel-blue-spring-kit-with-billet-spring-housing-for-2003-2007-ford-powerstroke-60l.html">Sinister Diesel Blue Spring Kit with Billet Spring Housing for 2003-2007 Ford Powerstroke 6.0L</a>
