              <h3 class="name">
                <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel-charge-pipe-kit-for-2017-ford-powerstroke-67l.html">Sinister Diesel Charge Pipe Kit for 2017-2026 Ford Powerstroke 6.7L</a>
