              <img src="/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/F144812844.jpg" alt="">
              <div class="disc-badge" aria-hidden="true">%</div>
            </a>
            <div class="body">
              <h3 class="name">
                <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel-complete-blue-package-for-2011-2016-ford-powerstroke-67l.html">Complete Blue Package for 2011-2016 Ford Powerstroke 6.7L</a>
              </h3>
              <div class="sku">SKU: SD-CBK-6.7P</div>
              <div class="price"><span class="sale"></span><span class="was"></span></div>
              <a class="btn view" href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel-complete-blue-package-for-2011-2016-ford-powerstroke-67l.html">View Product</a>
